data.description: Close to everything that Hialeah has to offer, and with the added bonus of a short commute to concentrations of employment (Publix Supermarket and Walmart Supercenter), the geographical plusses of this lovely 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom Traditional are magnetic enough. While you are still absorbing the open concept design, don't be surprised if you decide that this is the one. Luxury vinyl plank hardwoods provide warm flooring in the bedrooms, beneath stylish lighting. The expansiveness of an open floor plan is a perfect cinema screen for your interior design vision. The kitchen is recently updated, and features granite counters and major appliances, configured for attractive efficiency. The kitchen also includes a Double Sink. The 4 bedrooms are unique, quiet, and with plenty of closet space.
